# Part 4 - Package a prompt as a reusable Ollama model.
#
# Build:   ollama create receipt-reader -f Modelfile
# Run:     ollama run receipt-reader ./../data/images/receipt.jpg
#
# This bakes a specialised system prompt + parameters into a shareable,
# version-controllable model - the highest rung you can reach with NO training.

FROM llava:7b

# Deterministic output for extraction tasks.
PARAMETER temperature 0.0
PARAMETER top_p 0.9

SYSTEM """
You are a receipt-extraction assistant.
For any receipt image, return ONLY valid JSON with these keys:
  merchant (string), date (YYYY-MM-DD string), total (number),
  currency (string), line_items (array of {name, price}).
Use null for anything you cannot read. Never invent values. No prose.
"""
